title: Ash - Discography [DB]
description:
This is a discography from Northern Ireland descendants Ash, featuring the following:

Trailer [1994]
1977 [1996]
Nu-Clear Sounds [1998]
Free All Angels [2001]
Meltdown [2004]
Twilight Of The Innocents [2007]

Unplugged @ Sirius [2002]
Tokyo Blitz (mp3 rip) [2001]

And a (very nearly) complete singles and B-sides compilation as well which is surprisingly rare, considering the quality of this band, and extremely hard to find on my part! 

And it's also got their greatest hits in the form of "Intergalactic Sonic 7's". This could take a while to download so please be patient!
